<div class="content mb-10">
  <h1>Submit Your Entry</h1>
</div>

<div class="text-bold mb-10">
  <p>Submit an Open Education Week entry in two easy steps: </p>
</div>

<div class="flex justify-evenly mb-10 flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6">
  <div class="rounded bg-white lg:shadow lg:w-1/3 pt-4 pb-10 px-10 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-4">
    {{svg-jar "step1" class="h-auto inline-block"}}
    <p class="text-sm">Tell us about yourself and your institution/organization.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="rounded bg-white lg:shadow lg:w-1/3 pt-4 pb-10 px-10 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-4">
    {{svg-jar "step2" class="h-auto inline-block"}}
    <p class="text-sm">Describe your contribution, provide a link, and upload an image.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="p-4 bg-green-900 text-left flex flex-col gap-4 border border-green-400 border-1 rounded-2xl mb-10">
  <p>Other important information regarding your submission:</p>

  <div class="flex flex-row justify-start items-baseline">
    <span class="inline-flex w-4 mr-2">
      {{svg-jar "check-circle-solid" class="h-4 flex-shrink fill-current text-green-400 mt-1"}}
    </span>
    <p class="inline">All entries must be CC licensed.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-row justify-start items-baseline">
    <span class="inline-flex w-4 mr-2">
      {{svg-jar "check-circle-solid" class="h-4 flex-shrink fill-current text-green-400 mt-1"}}
    </span>
    <p class="inline">Once your entry is approved, youâ€™ll receive a confirmation email including a link to edit your
    entry.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-row justify-start items-start">
    <span class="inline-flex w-4 mr-2">
      {{svg-jar "check-circle-solid" class="h-4 flex-shrink fill-current text-green-400 mt-1"}}
    </span>
    <p class="inline">The data collected by the OE Global is specifically used for Open Education Week
    (OEW) operational purposes and will be displayed on the OEW site.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-row justify-start items-baseline">
    <span class="flex w-4 mr-2">
      {{svg-jar "check-circle-solid" class="h-4 flex-shrink fill-current text-green-400 mt-1"}}
    </span>
    <p class="inline">For questions, please <a href="mailto:info@openeducationweek.org" class="inline-block">contact us</a> and we'll be happy to assist you.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div>
  <LinkTo @route="submit.general" class="button-main">Get Started</LinkTo>
</div>

